description:
The legendary writer, comedian, producer & actor Donnell Rawlings stopped by the 85 South Show while headlining a weekend in Atlanta. Of course we asked him about what happened in Philly, what it was like working with Dave Chappelle & the Def Jam days. This episode is a classic! Download, leave a comment, subscribe - then let your cousin's sister listen! #85SouthShow
